    Guidelines
  </h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Display icons at either `16px` or `24px`
    </li>
    <li>
      Use `16px` icons by default in product interfaces
    </li>
    <li>
      Consider using `24px` icons in product interfaces for empty states
    </li>
    <li>
      Take care if choosing to display icons at sizes other than `16px` and
      `24px`
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    There may be cases where 16px and 24px values don't fit a design - Flight
    icons can be resized in these cases but be aware that the design is not
    optimized for values other than these.
  </p>
</div>
