<div class="mt-8 prose prose-lg text-gray-800 pb-6">
  <h4 class="ds-h4">
    Updating existing interfaces
  </h4>
  <ul class="ds-ul">
    <li class="ds-li">
      Where the current icon size is less than or equal to `20px`, replace icons
      with `16px` versions
    </li>
    <li class="ds-li">
      If the size of icon to be replaced is at least `21px`, first try to
      replace it with a `24px` version
    </li>
    <li class="ds-li">
      <i>
        If 24px seems too large, consider dropping down to 16px and reworking
        the interface for a better fit
      </i>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
